      <title>众议院议长邀请特朗普于 3 月 4 日向国会发表讲话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-25/house-speaker-invites-trump-to-address-congress-on-march-4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国众议院议长迈克·约翰逊邀请唐纳德·特朗普总统于 3 月 4 日在国会联席会议上发表讲话，为特朗普重返白宫后首次向议员发表重要讲话做好准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-25/house-speaker-invites-trump-to-address-congress-on-march-4</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2025 22:25:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
